content: Great fun. Owned it on Amazon app store but had to repurchase it here on Google Play Store.
The game is good, as other 10tons games, but like some other players, I lost my progress twice...
Love this game but no sound on Huawei P20 pro. Update - now have sound - thank you
Really enjoyed the game however; it rest my levels back to the beginning.... TWICE. I'll give it 5 stars as soon as I can complete the game without loosing my progress.

I love the game, but why do I keep losing my progress? I don't want to keep 
playing the same levels over. Please fix this.
Love it!!!!!!!
Simple, fun puzzles, moderate challenge (only halfway through the game atm) no frustrating get-stuck spots and best of all NO i  app purchases so the game doesnt go on well past your interest level.
NO SOUND - S8 PLUS
This is just a cute game I enjoy
Love it!
Great puzzle game! Some levels can be completed very quickly, but some keep you trying for ages. I like the added star mechanic to add an extra level of difficulty to each level.
I love the game. I bought it on Android and iOS. However, in Android version (I have Nexus 5), I just keep losing my progress and have to start from the beginning! Please fix it
Beautiful sound and visuals, great experience and a really good energy.
Cute, sometimes challenging, and fun. I love this game and the second one as well. Good job. ðŸ˜„
Works great! Easy to follow directions but still challenges the player.

This game will charm the pants off you. Well designed in every aspect. Few of the puzzles will really stump you after you get the hang of it, but it is very entertaining and there are a lot of puzzles. I always looked forward to playing it, now that I am done I will buy the sequel. I do wish it had cloud saving and an undo button, though, twice I accidentally finished puzzles without grabbing all the stars, which meant I needed to redo them.
I don't have much time to play any games, but since I'm so in love with this game I make time to play it, I can't stop. Best game ever.
My daughter and I love this game! It's the best game by far!
Lost progress twice now. Not going to try for a third time. Minus 2 stars for that.
Fun simple mechanics, levels are a bit random in difficulty though.
I dont ever play phone games. After playing this game I cant put my phone down. I need to join joining hands anonymous.
Superb game! Love it!
Get this game asap
Some steps are a little hard, but still fun.
This game is adorable, and my 4 year old loves it!
Says Open feint needs an active connection. With a black screen and wont go any father.

I loved this game, but now I notticed it isn't working. It just starts and tells me there is an error, that I'm not connected and feint needs to be connected. Everything is in black but I can hear the game's sounds :P  I'm on a Galaxy Nexus with Android 4.2
Open feint keeps causing the game to crash my phone before the game even starts up. Please remove it.
This game is off the chain get if not you stupid
Really fun and mind boggling
This game is amazing! U guys need to promote this game to be in front of Google play!
Fun and addicting
Fun logic game. Challenging enough to hold my attention.
Unnecessary permissions.
Ok

Cute, clever, simple, addictive. In short - highly recommended. Can't understand why this app is so unknown... The only bad thing I can think of is marketing - this is an "obscured hit app" - put it in the front page and it would skyrocket no doubt.
Quality graphics and enjoyable challenges
Very fun, interesting and unique puzzle game
Just finished all puzzles. Very addictive
great game. repurchase for me. bought on webos also
Really nicely done game and challenging also. I discovered this game by accident while browsing Appbrain and glad I did! Google needs to showcase this new game.

For puzzle lovers out there, this is a must game for u.. it is very interesting and creative in terms of its logic, graphics and gameplay. Sounds and Musics are great too. Works flawless on my galaxy s2. 10tons developer never let me down... Keep up the good job ! hope that Sparkle and Mirel 2 will come !
